<div id="header" class="container-fluid dark bluebg">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-6">
			<%= image_tag("logo2.png", class: "logo2", alt: "Logo of Trevor AI") %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-6 hidden-xs">
			<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
				<li class="active"><%= link_to "Trevor AI".html_safe, root_path %></li>
				<li><%= link_to "Web", web_path %></li>
				<li><%= link_to "App", app_path %></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="intro-bot" class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<h1 class="text-center">Find time for everything you want to do,<br/><underline>in a natural way</underline></h1>
		<div class="chatbox">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="bubble bubble-self pull-right">
					<p><strong>Trevor,</strong> I have to buy groceries</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="bubble bubble-trevor">
					<p>Here are the best available times...</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="bubble bubble-actions">
					<ul>
						<li>After work</li>
						<li>Tomorrow morning</li>
						<li>Wednesday at 3 pm</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr class="margin"/>
		<div class="col-md-3 availability vertical-align">
			<p class="text-right"><strong>Will be</strong> available on:</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6 availability vertical-align center-block">
			<%= image_tag('html_icon.png') %>
			<%= image_tag('messenger_icon.png') %>
			<%= image_tag('slack_icon.png') %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-3 availability vertical-align">
			<p>In January-ish..probably<br/>
				<span class="faded">with Telegram, Kik, Cortana, Alexa, and more, right after that.</span></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


<div id="meettrevor" class="container-fluid section dark bluebg">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<h3 class="text-left">Trevor is a personal assistant<br/><span class="faded">that connects your task lists with your calendar,</span><br/>to help you manage your time,<br/><span class="faded">the same way you already do in your mind.</span></h3>
			</div>
			
			<div id="" class="download col-md-6">
			<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->
				<div id="mc_embed_signup">
					<form action="//linkedin.us12.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=5418fe1e541a0e43db9c54656&amp;id=e1e62066d1" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
					    <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">
					<div class="indicates-required"><span class="asterisk">*</span> indicates required</div>
					<div class="mc-field-group">
						<label for="mce-EMAIL">Email Address  <span class="asterisk">*</span>
					</label>
						<input type="email" value="" placeholder="Email" name="EMAIL" class="required email" id="mce-EMAIL" onclick="mixpanel.track('Email Field 1 Clicked');">
					</div>
						<div id="mce-responses" class="clear">
							<div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
							<div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
						</div>    <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
					    <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;" aria-hidden="true"><input type="text" name="b_5418fe1e541a0e43db9c54656_e1e62066d1" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
					    <div class="clear"><input type="submit" value="Get Early Access" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button" onclick="mixpanel.track('Email Field 1 Submitted');"></div>
					    </div>
					</form>
				</div>
				
			<!--End mc_embed_signup-->
			</div>
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


